data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!!   CORNER UNIT in desirable Pinewood Village.  This 2 bedroom, 2 bath is ready for new owner wanting to add personal touches to this spacious split floor plan condo.  Unit features large rooms, including living/dining room combination, master bedroom with en-suite bath and walk-in closet, second bedroom with walk-in closet, Florida room with utility closet. Just outside your front door is  the covered carport and dedicated outdoor storage room. The community offers a clubhouse, heated pool with sundeck and more and is located near restaurants, shopping, recreation, entertainment, Countryside Mall and just a short drive to Dunedin, Safety Harbor, airports and beautiful gulf beaches. This well-maintained community showcases a heated pool with sundeck lounging area and clubhouse.
